reviewText: The legends DVD, Vale Tudo grappling from one of the best in the world. DVD is structured in a simple format and techniques are explain thoroughly.

I bought this hoping I would pick up some street fighting tactics. For the most part it didn't dissappoint. This isn't really about competition BJJ, this is about Street BJJ. This one is pretty badass, I'd recommend it.
NOTE** these guys got deep accents. Like portuguese accents, but you can still make out their english.
